{"tid":1550763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！！大家一齊煲大新屋嶺嘅事！","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:51:02.000Z","uid":79655,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4323a354b890a0894a28701cf61f671bcc3fc7d3","tid":1550763,"uid":79655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察扣押示威者時輪姦香港女市民<br />\n<br />\n香港警察選擇性扣押後生香港女市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">將呢兩句譯成其它語言去各大平台文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔好同我講fact check！check你老母啊</span>"},{"pid":"bc5caada668f9804812c1ff42642fa04309a2ee4","tid":1550763,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"706e723d1701c5d45ce0930b6927f778a9ec31b6","tid":1550763,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻人嗰啲藍絲扮架，支持送中，支持警察架"},{"pid":"89907aeec17913d58148f1c988f0172b9dc4c755","tid":1550763,"uid":79655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:33:03.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca111685a99c913d29e77023a4927cd7986430e9","tid":1550763,"uid":79655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"706e723d1701c5d45ce0930b6927f778a9ec31b6","tid":1550763,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻人嗰啲藍絲扮架，支持送中，支持警察架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 防暴 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 綠衫狗 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔係暴徒 唔使防暴！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bf6e14a7a07d064063a841fe40f45b48e613ea3f","tid":1550763,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"7c33ac7d9822fcbe67c0a7729faf0d11dab794dc","tid":1550763,"uid":79655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推到有人譯</span>"},{"pid":"2be5c97d26d335a06c6687a9e2aa793061599910","tid":1550763,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74af3441e0c06c13b9bbc3bf853fa4d66430b02e","tid":1550763,"uid":79655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"推到有人譯！"},{"pid":"21d8e6c44e46bae21ec7a41ca680e38facb4d957","tid":1550763,"uid":156666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:35:32.000Z","msg":"[而家決定]左膠割定唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1550759/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1550759/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"48d7ca4b123b9f418f38ba5498183753b3130e15","tid":1550763,"uid":110331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">We may have lost a battle but NOT the war<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地今日機場喺輸左但場運動未</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日美領大遊行要齊人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要過左五大訴求就會成真！<br />\n政府要係2020實行真。普選立法會<br />\n侵犯人權的官員人和家庭成員簽證可被撤銷，外資可被凍結！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmfHUdC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmfHUdC.png&h=89bc45e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksEYsyD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksEYsyD.png&h=ab62bc0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">呢個先喺真真正正嘅END GAME<br />\n未清楚咩事可以睇下面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">草案要求中國政府履行承諾，容許港人治港、高度自治，並且確保香港人可以通過普選，選出行政長官及立法會所有議席，當中特別設下「時限」，要求在2020年普選立法會。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2。</span></span></span><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">特別警告香港若就23條立法，除非可證明不影響港人及外籍居民的人權，否則美國政府可中止《香港政策法》等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">3。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">侵犯人權的及損害香港自治的官員及人士的清單。名單裡的人在美國的資產可被凍結、個人和家庭成員的簽證可被撤銷，要求美國總統調查及制裁打壓香港自由的官員。會交代香港是否有官員因協助侵犯人權而需要受制裁。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">這有助國際社會持續監察香港的狀況，如能每年通過查證，實際上等同美國年年為一國兩制投下信任一票，這一方面有助有助保障香港高度自治，同時亦會加強國際社會對香港的信心。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DYm9M6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DYm9M6.png&h=40ab8a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LehviFs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLehviFs.png&h=cadff255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">未簽聯署即做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC4aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=2a6cc24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日12點遮打花園見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7A6LR0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7A6LR0y.png&h=81aa1e4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9af97d9944e46b3477ef4f79cb98c616c846fd9","tid":1550763,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1330bbb975344edd6aaa1a999cd11141135892a6","tid":1550763,"uid":24397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d8f16a8bb9e2de13b57a3d63207921549af33c0","tid":1550763,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"你推完都唔撚會有人信"},{"pid":"f56996746201ef661448fc7fdd1655f2175d6fd7","tid":1550763,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"Twitter 先有外國人開始話我地呢邊都有fake news...譯做英文文宣出去唔係唔得,要加懷疑2個字<br />\n如果唔係我地信佢地唔信仲要當左f